Package: va.gov
Title: VA Open Data (Socrata SODA) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the VA Open Data Socrata SODA API.
    Covers catalog listing, search, veteran population, benefits, compensation,
    expenditures, facilities, home loans, PTSD research, and diagnoses.
    Includes LLM context injection via va_context().
